Help on module WorldMap:

NAME
    WorldMap - Main class that runs the world map

FILE
    EnvironmentSimulationPython/WorldMap.py

FUNCTIONS
    display_map()
        Displays the main map
        Contains the game loop that:
            Calls all sprite group updates
            Reproduces all sprites
            Display populations
            Allows user to place sprites
            Calls the pause menu
    
    empty_all_groups()
        Empties all sprites from all groups

AUTHOR
    Matthew Severance
